      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Selecting this will restart the session, and any work in progress will be lost."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "配下のセッションはすべて停止されます。フォルダ自体は削除されません。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All sessions under it will be stopped. The folder itself will not be deleted."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "開始 %@": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Started %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "変更は次回セッション開始から反映されます。OFF の場合、コマンド承認プロンプトが出るため自律実行が止まり得ます。ON（フルアクセス／bypass）は承認なしでコマンドを実行します。信頼できるプロジェクトでのみ有効にしてください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Changes take effect from the next session. When off, command approval prompts may appear and pause autonomous execution. ON (full access / bypass) executes commands without approval — enable it only for projects you trust."
          }
        }
      }
    },
